Technical Document: Calculator App

1. Overview

The Calculator App is a simple Python-based application that performs basic arithmetic operations, including addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division. It is designed for command-line interaction and provides user-friendly error handling.

2. Features

Addition, subtraction, multiplication, and division operations.

Handles divide-by-zero errors gracefully.

Simple and intuitive command-line interface.

Lightweight with minimal dependencies.
